    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Solid, honest driver in fair condition with the kind of wear you\u2019d expect for its age. It\u2019s not a show car, but it\u2019s a practical, usable vehicle that still presents decently and offers good value for someone who wants dependable transportation without overspending. A great fit for a buyer who appreciates a straightforward car priced realistically.",
