    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid older vehicle in fair condition. It shows normal wear for its age, with noticeable cosmetic imperfections inside and out, but it remains a usable, presentable car for someone looking for basic transportation. Expect some signs of age, minor issues, and maintenance items that may need attention over time, but it is not being represented as a fixer-upper or a mint example. A buyer should expect an honest, average-condition vehicle that has been used and shows it, priced accordingly.",
