      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an approachable price. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values practicality, a low entry cost, and solid everyday utility over perfection. A smart opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone seeking inexpensive wheels with plenty of life left to give.",
