      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s a great option for someone who wants a cheap runabout, a first project, or something to tinker with and make their own. Priced to make sense, offered by a seller who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with. If you want simple, honest value and don\u2019t mind a bit of rough-around-the-edges character, this one could be a really handy buy.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, straight-shooting driver with strong project or commuter potential. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the gearbox engages as it should, and the chassis still feels planted enough to be a worthwhile platform for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Cosmetically it shows its age and needs attention, but that also means you\u2019re not paying for fluff\u2014just a usable, mechanically promising car with plenty of upside. A great candidate for a budget build, parts runner, or daily with character.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
